				["Top"] = 933.9998779296875,
				["Black"] = {
					"[spell: chains of eternity]\n\nAniihilating Smash\n\nSomeone with Everbeating Heart needs to help soak chains marker\n\nHeroic: Help Soak Puddles, x1 spawns with chains\n\n\n2/6/19 worked\n", -- [1]
					"Running Fight\nBring druids for roar\nEye rotates with lazer, have to do a lap through the teleporter\nKill Valk add, shreads tanks, hard swap to it\n\n\nTanks have to mitigate Death Link else raidwide dmg\n\nLust: 3rd Phase\n\nMarks:\nTriangle - Chain Soaks, Where ranged stacks for chains so tank doesnt get hit\n\n2/6/21 works\n", -- [2]
					"Interupt Song of Dissolution\n\nFragments of Destiny stack together, wait till crystals fall off\n\nPurple soak x1\nBlue help soak\n\nDPS first two angles evenly\nHero: when the third angle come down\n\nDont soak Aradne's Falling Strike if you have Link Essence\n\n\n2/7/20 Worked", -- [3]
					"Lust: At pull or to help catch healing up\nHealing Cooldowns:\n\n\nDance on the Pizza Slices\nNeed lock gate to get across pizza\nBrands make enemies weak- also do damage to raid, use during add phase otherwise stand out\n\nHeroic: Stay out of the blue swirleys\n\nScale up to 2/5/14, groups are the round you help break chains\nBring DKs to grip ads", -- [4]
					"Hokey Pokey Boss\nEveryone congregates in the middle hopping not to get knocked off the platform\nThey all face inward\nPerson with black orb over head faces outward, with back to the raid\n\nDPS orb when shield drops\nDodge blue swirls\n\nUse orange and yellow markers to match DBM\nTanks call out hold for suffering\n\n\n2/6/21", -- [5]
					"The Pug Breaker\n\nNeed to be 3 rows in during phase 1 and 3\nMark jumping points for Tanks\nBalls roll across platform and 1 shot people\n\"A death spike is coming for you\" - watch out for the balls\nRed swirleys are where balls are going to spawn\n\n2/4/8 - Extra healer was good\n2/6/19 - Worked\n\nSave lust for the last phase\n\nHeroic:\n4 ppl will spawn with a trap\nIf you drop it in the middle of the raid, everybody will die\nLimited amount of time to drop it in the right spot\nDrop on left for P1\nDrop on tank mechanic top-right P2 and beyond", -- [6]
					"Energy 75, 50, 25\n\nHit 0 Energy then take two big hits (ring, ams, etc)\ntake him into the battery for recharge\n\nVen diagram, olympic ring the big yellow circles\n\nDPS check\n\nTank Buster:\n\n\nLust: Beginning or after third battery\n\n\n2/6/18 Worked", -- [7]
					"Cheese:\nExtra heals allows tank to soak add and dot\n\"Smooths out fight\"\n\nAssign CW spin + 1 backup to CCW spin\n\nHero:\nP3\n", -- [8]
					"3 DPS and 1 Healer go down\nSend melee and hunters (lots of movement, dps loss)\nport back at 60 & 20%\n\nDont get frozen\nSoak white circles\nBring adds to tank\n\n\n", -- [9]
					"2/4/11\n\nP1\nUse chain if stacks to high", -- [10]
					"//Quality Mythic Plus\nmythicplus and heals<=0 and (hoa or soa) and mprating>=1000\n\n//Heroic Raid Spam Filter\nheroic and sod and age<180\n\n//Heroic Sylvanus\nheroic and sod and defeated>=9 and not boss[\"sylvanas windrunner\"]\n\n", -- [11]
					"", -- [12]
					"", -- [13]
					"2/6/19 Worked\n\n", -- [14]
				},
